接口 RecordIterator<T>

所有超级接口:

public interface RecordIterator<T>
extends Iterator<T>, Closeable
Iterator over records in the storage backend. Behaves like a normal iterator with an additional close method so that resources associated with this iterator can be released.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
